  \{t:"Project",d:"easy",q:"Who owns and prioritizes the product backlog in Scrum?",opts:["Scrum Master","Developer","Product Owner","Stakeholder"],a:2,exp:"The Product Owner manages and prioritizes the product backlog to maximize the value delivered by the team."\},\
